{"tid":1288342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：對大專院校學生會拒見政府感到失望","createTime":"2019-07-05T15:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T10:16:51.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":718,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3e0d26e467262b6941774f8627b8ff3ca68156","tid":1288342,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"對於有大專院校的學生會，要求政府如果能滿足兩項要求，包括不向反修例示威者作追究，以及要公開會面，便可以考慮和政府對話，<span style=\"color: red;\">行政會議成員湯家驊表示感到失望，認為錯過對話機會，無助化解嚴重對立，希望雙方就會面模式溝通，但要妥協法治是相當高難度的要求。</span><br />\n<br />\n湯家驊表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">七一當日出現很多違法行為，包括強行進入處所、刑事毀壞等，用政治理由妨礙檢控是違反《基本法》條文和法治精神。</span><br />\n<br />\n另一名行會成員張國鈞則說最重要是有對話機會讓特首知道想法，呼籲學生不要拘泥是否閉門，會議不會有陰謀詭計，閉門見面可以更坦誠表達意見，希望學生重新考慮、不要有前設。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466812-20190705.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466812-20190705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=ea290741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466812-20190705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a299f8d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466812-20190705.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4c2bfb47d11b10e2d55891aead226e3b415855","tid":1288342,"uid":164050,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ded537448ce778e4b991a4fb51c3ac0daff2bfc","tid":1288342,"uid":4496,"like":440,"dislike":0,"score":440,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:03:46.000Z","msg":"對湯渣衰十一投共感到失望"},{"pid":"3d2b104352f57564e2c5f34d51bf0d52cb39e791","tid":1288342,"uid":2545,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"quote":{"pid":"4ded537448ce778e4b991a4fb51c3ac0daff2bfc","tid":1288342,"uid":4496,"like":440,"dislike":0,"score":440,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-0