78,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:02:35.000Z","msg":"轉向 Google，緊隨「湯家驊」的，竟是「衰十一」。湯大狀不解，問：「咩叫衰十一？」得知答案後，他一臉不屑，繼而靜默。有傳他被掌握了黑材料，故言論受制於人，他否認：「有人抹黑我。」"},{"pid":"ff88b44d1acf81385ade50af1a40b7ed5b32451b","tid":1288342,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ded537448ce778e4b991a4fb51c3ac0daff2bfc","tid":1288342,"uid":4496,"like":440,"dislike":0,"score":440,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:03:46.000Z","msg":"對湯渣衰十一投共感到失望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fab90ab21aa69ca49a249e270010efe49a72da","tid":1288342,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:07:09.000Z","msg":"淚灑雪廠街"},{"pid":"0550bf2b5687f1131727f09926fc3f69b7233bb2","tid":1288342,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:16:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GLyZFiCTq-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGLyZFiCTq-M&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=301ab112\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GLyZFiCTq-M</a>"},{"pid":"f074c128525ebb0225cf22813b3185942944d6fa","tid":1288342,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:54:10.000Z","msg":"我哋做乜要見<br />\n五大訴求講得好清楚<br />\n而家係仆街政府要回應<br />\n無人可以代替我哋妥協"},{"pid":"d4a548a2b093c0b8095378eacad850147555d689","tid":1288342,"uid":192034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T00:05:57.000Z","msg":"對白劇本都安排好哂，佢地都係等各大學生會拒絕之後就講依番說話，比大家覺得學生萌塞唔肯溝通，又係依啲技倆，好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3265241b6fcead76030d84a80dffcafdba7056e","tid":1288342,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep